title: Grateful Dead Live at Rich Stadium on 1992-06-06
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Grey-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Althea, It's All Over Now, Friend Of The Devil, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Ramble On Rose, Let It Grow

Set 2

Iko Iko, Estimated Prophet-> The Same Thing-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> The Wheel-> Throwing Stones-> One More Saturday Night, E:Baba O'Riley-> E: Tomorrow Never Knows

"Take A Step Back," between Masterpiece and Ramble On

reviews.review_text: 1992 Summer Tour Saw this concert, drove up to buffalo ,parked. Inside me and 2 friends jumped onto the floor, got dosed. The playing that nite was great. After the show we got our camping gear out and camped on a grassy hill just outside the parking lot. They had the lights on in rich stadium and we watched smoke linger out of that place for hours. I the morning we headed for Ohio.
